HEADWORD: Kiddy
<hw>Kid"dy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To deceive; to
outwit; to hoax.</def> <mark>[Slang]</mark>
<rj><au>Dickens.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

