==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Kiddy
<hw>Kid"dy</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A young fellow; formerly, a low
thief.</def> <mark>[Slang, Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kiddyish</ent>⟦br⟧
